HiggsAudio GGML C++ runtime

This repository contains runtime source code only. It does not include
HiggsAudio model weights, generated audio, reference audio, or cached reference
codes.

Vendored dependencies:

- ggml: vendored as vendor/ggml or supplied with -DHIGGS_GGML_DIR. Follow the
  ggml license from that checkout. The current project submodule is tested at
  ggml v0.15.3.
- shine: vendored under third_party/shine. It is distributed under the GNU
  Library General Public License version 2; see its COPYING file.
- tokenizers.cpp: vendored under third_party/tokenizers.cpp. See its LICENSE,
  NOTICE, and THIRD_PARTY_NOTICES.md.
- miniaudio: vendored as third_party/miniaudio/miniaudio.h. The header offers a
  public domain / Unlicense or MIT-0 choice; see the license text embedded in
  the header.
